window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Mount Trilogy concludes with <i>Sinful Empire</i>! </p> <p>What's mine, I keep, and that includes Keira Kilgore. </p> <p>It's no longer enough to have her in my debt. No longer enough to own her body. </p> <p>I want something more. </p> <p>She can try to resist, but I'll never give her up. </p> <p>Nothing will keep us apart. </p> <p>Not her. Not my enemies. No one. </p> <p>Her debt will only be paid one way - with her heart. </p> <p><i>Sinful Empire</i> is the third and final book in the Mount Trilogy. </p>"; 
